DeathSteel::

He made his way to where Kaiser was located. He looked at him. "Here 
I am. I will take your actions to mean you wish to see what I am made 
of."  He had to think and choose his words carefully. "I shall be 
honored to fight one such as yourself. Bring honor to yourself this 
day."  He bowed to him. "This is a good day to die."
